metadata.name: Archangel defeats devil
metadata.description:
Here I want to introduce you not just an angel, but a holy Archangel, the protector of mankind, who defeats pure evil in the form of a snake skeleton. Grace, tenderness, incredible strength - all this is inherent in the true Archangel.

ALL BIDDERS RECEIVE A SPECIAL CHARACTER STAMP! Check the preview on the author's twitter page.

Art made by nicksuslin | 2022

Resolution - 3864x5520 px
